{"tid":1314933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［ 學術 ］係時候用戰術核顯卡","createTime":"2019-07-14T11:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T12:06:55.000Z","uid":269125,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b33a92133783602e3243bca0efc9595aaa739e8","tid":1314933,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:30:39.000Z","msg":"啲犬認為我地會出燃燒彈真係睇低我地<br />\n燃燒彈太cheap，戰鬥力太弱<br />\n我建議大家改用nvidia製既戰術核顯卡<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WRv8AaSmaBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWRv8AaSmaBY&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPaqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=751c7585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WRv8AaSmaBY</a><br />\n<br />\n內地同胞已經研究過nvidia既690系戰術核顯卡<br />\n一發就足夠毀滅航母<br />\n當然呢個只係誇大啦<br />\n<br />\n只係690功耗大，容易造成大爆炸<br />\n相信用嚟對癲咗既狗隻完全無問題<br />\n因此我號召各位連登巴絲打即時去收購回收店入面既舊690卡<br />\n後續機型既790、980都得，不過貴啲<br />\n<br />\n由於犬隻最近mon住連登<br />\n相信佢地好快會捕住去回收店既人<br />\n要買趁手，21號可用"},{"pid":"32f74d47fd1b6f40c6480a47b2e6b543c8080eab","tid":1314933,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:32:17.000Z","msg":"要買趁手 犬隻mon住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2999a1659467bd639de3c2e566501e839d0eca07","tid":1314933,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:33:43.000Z","msg":"要買趁手 犬隻mon住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2872b6de3594fd5ef17b105065a227aab0d65ca2","tid":1314933,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:36:16.000Z","msg":"要買趁手 犬隻mon住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8365c31f04e5f1d00bcb8c7e5f54c2ea9cdef8","tid":1314933,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:42:58.000Z","msg":"要買趁手 犬隻mon住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e01f4f6a46322fa0bcacf9537a43f171439813","tid":1314933,